  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/c8f88434d54de208739c3b0846f6d75f.avif?t=1751521476\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras_big/c8f88434d54de208739c3b0846f6d75f.avif?t=1751521476 width=800 height=212 /></span>Trapped in a room of the Italian genial inventor, you need to think out of the box to solve logical enigmas written in a book and escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the answers, unlock the Cryptex, and see what awaits you in the next room!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/b2a8bbefc101f3017b6fb5e47f3a77ae.poster.avif?t=1751521476\" width=614 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/b2a8bbefc101f3017b6fb5e47f3a77ae.webm?t=1751521476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/b2a8bbefc101f3017b6fb5e47f3a77ae.mp4?t=1751521476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/9722870c8b899b9377ca99b00d3ea8dd.avif?t=1751521476\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras_big/9722870c8b899b9377ca99b00d3ea8dd.avif?t=1751521476 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Da Vinci Cryptex</strong> is a brainteasing game consisting of 50 unique riddles, the more you go on, the harder to solve the puzzles </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, how many enigmas can you crack? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/615ad496be04a7845f3a94dfa28f8f83.avif?t=1751521476\" width=614 height=178 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Warning: this IQ game may be addictive!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/2b52f752f27005c28360ccb090e77ec5.avif?t=1751521476\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras_big/2b52f752f27005c28360ccb090e77ec5.avif?t=1751521476 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 50 unique handcrafted puzzles </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hints available (click the bulb button to get a hint) </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Astonishing graphics∑</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Captivating background music</strong> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>If you're a fan of puzzles, word games, brain thinking, mind games, logic riddles, and enigmas, The Da Vinci Cryptex is the game for you!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521476\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras_big/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521476 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of  <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/c8f88434d54de208739c3b0846f6d75f.avif?t=1751521476\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras_big/c8f88434d54de208739c3b0846f6d75f.avif?t=1751521476 width=800 height=212 /></span>Trapped in a room of the Italian genial inventor, you need to think out of the box to solve logical enigmas written in a book and escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the answers, unlock the Cryptex, and see what awaits you in the next room!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/b2a8bbefc101f3017b6fb5e47f3a77ae.poster.avif?t=1751521476\" width=614 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/b2a8bbefc101f3017b6fb5e47f3a77ae.webm?t=1751521476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/b2a8bbefc101f3017b6fb5e47f3a77ae.mp4?t=1751521476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/9722870c8b899b9377ca99b00d3ea8dd.avif?t=1751521476\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras_big/9722870c8b899b9377ca99b00d3ea8dd.avif?t=1751521476 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Da Vinci Cryptex</strong> is a brainteasing game consisting of 50 unique riddles, the more you go on, the harder to solve the puzzles </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, how many enigmas can you crack? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/615ad496be04a7845f3a94dfa28f8f83.avif?t=1751521476\" width=614 height=178 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Warning: this IQ game may be addictive!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/2b52f752f27005c28360ccb090e77ec5.avif?t=1751521476\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras_big/2b52f752f27005c28360ccb090e77ec5.avif?t=1751521476 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 50 unique handcrafted puzzles </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hints available (click the bulb button to get a hint) </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Astonishing graphics∑</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Captivating background music</strong> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>If you're a fan of puzzles, word games, brain thinking, mind games, logic riddles, and enigmas, The Da Vinci Cryptex is the game for you!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521476\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras_big/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521476 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of  <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>",
